headline: AppLovin to Announce Second Quarter 2025 Results
summary: PALO ALTO, Calif., July 02, 2025--AppLovin Corporation, (NASDAQ: APP) ("AppLovin" or the "Company") the leading marketing platform, today announced it will report financial results for the second quarter ended June 30, 2025 on Wednesday, August 6, 2025 after the U.S. stock market closes.
